Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.26,0:01:17.47,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}和白天的疾风骤雨
Dialogue: 6,0:01:17.43,0:01:22.18,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}波长同步
Dialogue: 7,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.06,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}虽然无法浪漫地
Dialogue: 8,0:01:24.60,0:01:30.19,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}说出动听的话语
